        <Parent_String>Ottoman (style) [300021614], Anatolian Islamic styles and periods after Manzikert [300244021], Islamic World dynastic styles and periods [300021520], Islamic World, The [300021516], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
